data.description: 4-bdrm Cape Cod home on a double lot, w/ a huge garage. Built in 2007, garage is equipped with a 50-amp service, Modine gas heater, insulated walls, attic with stair access, 8-ft doors. Ample parking provided by 6-in reinforced concrete slabs adjacent to & behind the garage. Interior features a seamless open concept kitchen/living rm w/ professionally refinished hardwood floors. Recent upgrades: new carpeting and freshly painted interior. Both bathrooms have undergone full renovations, new flooring, countertops, tub, tiles, fixtures, and more. The kitchen includes modern appliances. Noteworthy updates include a new picture window in the living rm & front bedroom, a new ultra-efficient hybrid Wi-Fi water heater , prof. exterior painting, roof replace (tear-off) front of the home in 2017.
